<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><u>Associate Mentor Updates</u></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Hey&nbsp;</b><font face="arial"><b>{!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Here are a few IMPORTANT updates regarding your application to be an Associate Mentor role this summer.&nbsp;</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b><u><br></u></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b><u>1) Final Job Placement Allocation</u></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial" size="2">Thank you for attending AM training last week! It was lovely meeting you and I hope you are excited to start your role over the summer period.&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To sign up to a wave please click</span></font></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial"><a href="http://goo.gl/forms/SQaAkJiyvMgnyuQL2"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"></span><font size="5">HERE</font></a></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font face="arial" size="2">We will be allocating all roles over the next 2 weeks and you will&nbsp;receive&nbsp;an email with the dates/times/venue for your placement and the name and contact details of your manager. Please note that not every area will be running waves 1-12 so please do pick a variety of locations and dates you will like to work on so we can find a wave for you!</font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><u>2) More emails coming.. sorry!</u></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font size="2">We have organised a range of back-up assessment events for those that were not able to make the initial assessment. THERE IS NO NEED for you to attend another assessment so please just ignore these emails! &nbsp;for those of you who submitted a late application or couldn't attend a previous session. &nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><u>3) If your going to be 18 or over by the end of August...</u></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">You will need to have a Disclosure and Barring Service Check (DBS). These could take up to 12 weeks to process so get yours started now! <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionsAMs.pdf">Click here for more information and next steps!</a></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>If you have any questions do get in touch with Ola at ola.awosika@the-challenge.org or call 07785623395.&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;">Thank you very much!!&nbsp;</b></div>]]></td>
</tr>
